Introduction

Hwiseo is a South Korean singer and actress signed with Grandline Group (GLG). She debuted on June 13, 2022, as a member of the girl group H1-KEY. She is also a member of the project girl group EL7Z UP.

On April 24, 2023, she participated in the survival show Queendom Puzzle and finished in 1st place earning her spot in the project girl group EL7Z UP. They made their debut on September 14, 2023, with their first mini album “7+Up”.
